

This directory contains:


** Two general routines to save GEOS-Chem timeseries into 4D bpch files:

 gc_combine_nd48.pro  -> to process stations.YYYYMMDD files
 gc_combine_nd49.pro  -> to process tsYYYYMMDD.bpch files (works with Met Fields too!)



** A timeseries tutorial:

 tutorial\DATA            -> contains data for the tutorial

 tutorial\timeseries_brief_tutorial.pdf  -> the tutorial. Some commands in 
                                            the text can be found in the 
                                            following routines:

 tutorial\comp_nd48_49.pro         -> batch to compare output from nd48 and 49
 tutorial\example_anim_ts.pro      -> example to produce animation
 tutorial\examples_manip_4d.pro    -> example to test 4D datainfo

